values:
Today my hands resemble that of a dead woman's. Maybe it's because I'm cold, or maybe I died last night & didn't realize it.

I'm going to buy Lauren's purse off of her because it's majorly cute & she hates it so woot woot!!

Thank you to Molly & Lauren for being the only people to add me back.

Lauren & I have art next period, but I don't feel like dealing with my project. I've already screamed at it & almost thrown it across the room. Who knows what today will hold.

Work tonight will suck as usual, but what's new? I really need to start looking for another job before I go karate on them all!!
